headline.print_headline: Red Bull Rivalry Overtakes Hamilton, Rosberg Spat
headline.main: Red Bull Rivalry Overtakes Hamilton, Rosberg Spat

lead_paragraph: For weeks the Formula One world has been riveted on a feud between championship contenders Nico Rosberg and Lewis Hamilton but after the Canadian Grand Prix on Sunday the Mercedes team mates have another rivalry to worry about.
